unidue.ub.statistics.analysis

Class EventAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • unidue.ub.statistics.analysis.EventAnalysis

  • @Entity
public class EventAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
    Plain old java object holding an analysis of one year and one document. The fields can be persisted.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Eike Spielberg

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      EventAnalysis()
      Builds a new instance of a EventAnalysis-object, setting the individual counters to 0 and the text fields to an empty string.
